  "title": "In Santos-SP, a man observed four round UFOs moving erratically at high speed [1994]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/07/03/in-santos-sp-a-man-observed-four-round-ufos-moving-erratically-at-high-speed-1994/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1os",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>MAY 16, 1994</strong>. Time: 01:10 am. Duration: 30 minutes. In the city of Santos, State of São Paulo, a man observed, for thirty minutes, four unidentified flying objects &#8220;crossing each other&#8217;s path at high speed&#8221;. According to the witness, the UFOs were above the city center at an altitude that he could not estimate. The UFOs were spherical, yellow, and had a &#8220;medium size&#8221;, flying at a &#8220;very fast&#8221; speed. The sighting was performed with the naked eye and under good visibility conditions.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.364. “Questionário sobre ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado em Santos, Estado de São Paulo</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
